'''Tosa Kokubun-ji''' is a [[Shingon]] Buddhist Temple located in {{ill|Nankoku, Kōchi|en|Nankoku, Kōchi|WD=Q861621|lt=Nankoku, Kōchi|1=Nankoku, Kōchi}}, {{ill|Japan|en|Japan|WD=Q17|lt=Japan|1=Japan}}. It is the 29th temple of the {{ill|Shikoku Pilgrimage|en|Shikoku Pilgrimage|WD=Q1972399|lt=Shikoku Pilgrimage|1=Shikoku Pilgrimage}}.<ref>{{Cite web|title=第29番札所 摩尼山 宝蔵院 国分寺 – （一社）四国八十八ヶ所霊場会|url=http://www.88shikokuhenro.jp/29kokubunji/|website=www.88shikokuhenro.jp|access-date=2020-05-26}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://www.worldcat.org/oclc/76788376|title=Kōchi-ken no rekishi sanpo|date=2006|publisher=Yamakawa Shuppansha|others=Kōchi-ken Kōtō Gakkō Kyōiku Kenkyūkai. Rekishi Bukai., 高知県高等学校教育研究会. 歴史部会.|isbn=4-634-24639-2|edition=1-han|location=Tōkyō|oclc=76788376}}</ref> It is also the {{ill|Tosa Province|en|Tosa Province|WD=Q857330|lt=Tosa Province|1=Tosa Province}} [[Sōja shrine]]

